fileSamples.statement: (a b : trav_label -> Prop) : reserve_init_clos (a ∪₁ b) ≡₁ reserve_init_clos a ∪₁ reserve_init_clos b.
fileSamples.conclusion: reserve_init_clos (a ∪₁ b) ≡₁ reserve_init_clos a ∪₁ reserve_init_clos b

fileSamples.statement:
(a b : trav_label -> Prop) : (a ∪₁ b) \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0))
≡₁ a \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
   ∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0))
   ∪₁ (b \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
       ∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0))).
fileSamples.conclusion:
(a ∪₁ b) \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0))
≡₁ a \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
   ∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0))
   ∪₁ (b \₁ action ↓₁ eq ta_reserve
       ∪₁ eq ta_reserve <*> (acts_set G ∩₁ (fun a0 : actid => is_init a0)))
